<div class="counted" id="p5_33_RelatedPartyDisclosures">
<span class="counterPrefix">10.</span>
<span class="title">Related Party Transactions</span>
<div class="noteTextBlock">
<div>As at 31 March 2025, included within trade debtors is an amount of £59,347 due from Finance Advice Group Ltd (Company No. 08951525), a company under common control. Additionally, an intercompany loan of £5,000 is receivable from the same entity. This loan is unsecured, interest-free, and repayable on demand.</div>
<div class="blank-line"/>
<div>During the year, commission payments totalling £1,469,649 were received from the above company. These were arm's length transactions and are treated appropriately as revenue in statement of profit and loss.</div>
</div>
</div>
